snippet.title: tint. Gameplay Snippet
snippet.description:
"tint." lets you solve puzzles by painting. Mix watercolors to match the origami - all at a soothing pace and in the comfort of your own garden studio. No timers, no countdowns, no points, and certainly no rush 😌🎨
https://apps.apple.com/us/app/tint/id1451786388
